title: Tennis no Ouji-sama: Another Story - Kako to Mirai no Message Specials
synopsis: These specials feature the Oshitari cousins in a Manzai (漫才) setup [a style of stand-up comedy in Japan, which usually involves two performers—a straight man (tsukkomi) and a funny man (boke)].
